#: ../../doc/changelog.rst:2
msgid "Changelog"
msgstr "更新日志"

#: ../../doc/changelog.rst:4
msgid "Changelog since the version 1.5.0."
msgstr "自 1.5.0 版本以来的更新日志。"

#: ../../doc/changelog.rst:7
msgid "2.0.0"
msgstr ""

#: ../../doc/changelog.rst:9
msgid "First major update after the initial stable version."
msgstr "初始稳定版本后的首次重大更新。"

#: ../../doc/changelog.rst:12 ../../doc/changelog.rst:75
#: ../../doc/changelog.rst:133 ../../doc/changelog.rst:159
#: ../../doc/changelog.rst:193 ../../doc/changelog.rst:236
#: ../../doc/changelog.rst:246
msgid "Update"
msgstr "更新"

#: ../../doc/changelog.rst:14
msgid "Official MacOS (Apple Clang) support."
msgstr "官方 MacOS（Apple Clang）支持。"

#: ../../doc/changelog.rst:16
msgid ""
"The library can be compiled with exceptions disabled (``-fno-exceptions``"
" or ``/EHs-c-``)."
msgstr ""
"该库可以在禁用异常的情况下编译（``-fno-exceptions`` 或 ``/EHs-c-``）。"

#: ../../doc/changelog.rst:18
msgid ""
"The interfaces depending on exceptions will be redirected to an error "
"handling macro defined by the user. Its default behaviour is calling "
"``std::terminate`` immediately."
msgstr ""
"依赖于异常的接口将被重定向到用户定义的错误处理宏。其默认行为是立即调用 ``std::terminate``。"

#: ../../doc/changelog.rst:21
msgid ""
"(Experimental) Listener for customizing error handling or recording "
"registered entities."
msgstr ""
"（实验性）用于自定义错误处理或记录已注册实体的监听器。"

#: ../../doc/changelog.rst:23
msgid ""
"Wrapper of AngelScript memory APIs (``script_allocator``) now can be used"
" in constant evaluation. It will automatically fallback to constexpr "
"allocation under this situation."
msgstr ""
"AngelScript 内存 API 的包装器（``script_allocator``）现在可以在常量求值中使用。"
"在这种情况下，它将自动回退到 constexpr 分配。"

#: ../../doc/changelog.rst:26
msgid ""
"Merge the extension library and core library, dropping parts that is not "
"customizable (see the Breaking Change part below)."
msgstr ""
"合并扩展库和核心库，移除了不可自定义的部分（请参见下面的重大变更部分）。"

#: ../../doc/changelog.rst:28
msgid "Now, the library is **completely header-only**."
msgstr "现在，该库是**完全头文件-only**的。"

#: ../../doc/changelog.rst:30
msgid "Add more tools for implementing script debugging functionality."
msgstr "添加更多用于实现脚本调试功能的工具。"

#: ../../doc/changelog.rst:31
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"Update I/O module to support formatting script types when ``<format>`` "
"header is available. It also provides tools for quick integration with "
"other formatting library like {fmt}."
msgstr ""
"更新 I/O 模块以支持在 ``<format>`` 头文件可用时格式化脚本类型。"
"它还提供了与其他格式化库（如 {fmt}）快速集成的工具。"

#: ../../doc/changelog.rst:34
msgid ""
"Unify implementation of binding generators to make the codebase easier to"
" maintain."
msgstr ""
"统一绑定生成器的实现，使代码库更易于维护。"

#: ../../doc/changelog.rst:36
msgid ""
"Decouple binding generator interfaces with complex AngelScript calling "
"conventions"
msgstr ""
"将绑定生成器接口与复杂的 AngelScript 调用约定解耦"

#: ../../doc/changelog.rst:38
msgid "Tools for comparing script objects."
msgstr "用于比较脚本对象的工具。"

#: ../../doc/changelog.rst:40
msgid "Enable CMake script to use local external package for developing offline."
msgstr "启用 CMake 脚本使用本地外部包进行离线开发。"

#: ../../doc/changelog.rst:42
msgid "Update compatibility with AngelScript 2.39 WIP."
msgstr "更新与 AngelScript 2.39 WIP 的兼容性。"

#: ../../doc/changelog.rst:44
msgid ""
"Compile-time validation for signatures of behaviours, callbacks, etc. You"
" can disable it by defining macro "
"``ASBIND20_CONFIG_NO_COMPILE_TIME_CHECKS``."
msgstr ""
"对行为、回调等签名进行编译时验证。"
"你可以通过定义宏 ``ASBIND20_CONFIG_NO_COMPILE_TIME_CHECKS`` 来禁用它。"

#: ../../doc/changelog.rst:47
msgid "Update RAII helpers."
msgstr "更新 RAII 辅助函数。"

#: ../../doc/changelog.rst:50 ../../doc/changelog.rst:113
#: ../../doc/changelog.rst:166 ../../doc/changelog.rst:205
msgid "Breaking Change"
msgstr "重大变更"

#: ../../doc/changelog.rst:52
msgid ""
"String tools and compressed pair are moved into the namespace "
"``asbind20::util``."
msgstr ""
"字符串工具和压缩对已移至命名空间 ``asbind20::util`` 中。"

#: ../../doc/changelog.rst:53
msgid "``as_allocator`` is renamed to ``script_allocator``."
msgstr "``as_allocator`` 已重命名为 ``script_allocator``。"

#: ../../doc/changelog.rst:54
msgid "**Extension library is removed**."
msgstr "**扩展库已移除**。"

#: ../../doc/changelog.rst:56
msgid ""
"Since asbind20 originated from a submodule of a personal project, many of"
" the extensions were built for a private repository. I decided to migrate"
" them to a separate open-source library in the future. Some of the "
"extensions, like string extraction helper and section loader, are merged "
"into the core library."
msgstr ""
"由于 asbind20 源自个人项目的子模块，许多扩展是为私有仓库构建的。"
"我决定将来将它们迁移到一个单独的开源库中。"
"一些扩展，如字符串提取辅助函数和分段加载器，已合并到核心库中。"

#: ../../doc/changelog.rst:60
msgid ""
"Use ``asbind20::objfirst`` / ``objlast`` to specify the position of "
"object pointer/reference, if you want to specify them explicitly, instead"
" of dealing with underlying calling convention details of AngelScript."
msgstr ""
"使用 ``asbind20::objfirst`` / ``objlast`` 来指定对象指针/引用的位置，"
"如果你想要显式指定它们，而不是处理 AngelScript 的底层调用约定细节。"

#: ../../doc/changelog.rst:64
msgid "Redesign lock wrapper to fit common C++ paradigm for shared lock."
msgstr "重新设计锁包装器以适配常见的 C++ 共享锁范式。"

#: ../../doc/changelog.rst:66
msgid ""
"Now message callback and exception translator are registered by global "
"functions, instead of ``asbind20::global``."
msgstr ""
"现在消息回调和异常转换器通过全局函数注册，而不是 ``asbind20::global``。"

#: ../../doc/changelog.rst:70
msgid "1.8.0"
msgstr ""

#: ../../doc/changelog.rst:72
msgid "2025-10-29"
msgstr ""

#: ../../doc/changelog.rst:77
msgid ""
"``script_invoke_result`` no longer stores the result inside it, now it "
"will get the result when user needs it (lazy evaluation)."
msgstr ""
"``script_invoke_result`` 不再将结果存储在其中，现在将在用户需要时获取结果（延迟求值）。"

#: ../../doc/changelog.rst:80
msgid ""
"According to benchmarks, this has the same performance as the handwritten"
" code retrieving values from AS interfaces directly. It is even slightly "
"faster than the plain handwritten code in some situation. Compared to "
"handwritten implementation, the implementation from previous version is "
"slower about 1% ~ 3%, and even worse when returning a value type with "
"expensive copy construction, such as a string with extremely huge "
"content."
msgstr ""
"根据基准测试，这与直接从 AS 接口检索值的手写代码具有相同的性能。"
"在某些情况下，它甚至比普通手写代码略快。"
"与手写实现相比，以前版本的实现慢了约 1% ~ 3%，"
"在返回具有昂贵拷贝构造的值类型时（例如包含极大内容的字符串），情况更糟。"

#: ../../doc/changelog.rst:85
msgid ""
"Experimental support for enum with custom underlying type in AngelScript "
"2.39 WIP."
msgstr ""
"AngelScript 2.39 WIP 中支持具有自定义底层类型的枚举的实验性功能。"

#: ../../doc/changelog.rst:86
msgid ""
"Utility for quickly implementing conversion rules for enums with "
"underlying type other than ``int`` such as ``std::byte``."
msgstr ""
"用于快速实现底层类型不是 ``int``（例如 ``std::byte``）的枚举的转换规则的工具。"

#: ../../doc/changelog.rst:88
msgid "Experimental support for script ``foreach``."
msgstr "对脚本 ``foreach`` 的实验性支持。"

#: ../../doc/changelog.rst:90
msgid ""
"``script_invoke_result`` now supports ``operator->`` for pointer type, "
"which is useful for accessing members of returned reference types."
msgstr ""
"``script_invoke_result`` 现在支持指针类型的 ``operator->``，"
"这对于访问返回的引用类型的成员很有用。"

#: ../../doc/changelog.rst:93
msgid "Expose ``get_context_result`` for easily retrieving result from context."
msgstr "公开 ``get_context_result`` 以便轻松从上下文中检索结果。"

#: ../../doc/changelog.rst:95
msgid "Add member function ``value_or`` for ``script_invoke_result``."
msgstr "为 ``script_invoke_result`` 添加成员函数 ``value_or``。"

#: ../../doc/changelog.rst:97
msgid "``script_invoke_result`` can be converted to ``std::optional``."
msgstr "``script_invoke_result`` 可以转换为 ``std::optional``。"

#: ../../doc/changelog.rst:98
msgid ""
"``script_invoke_result`` can be converted to ``std::expected`` if C++23 "
"is available."
msgstr ""
"如果 C++23 可用，``script_invoke_result`` 可以转换为 ``std::expected``。"

#: ../../doc/changelog.rst:100
msgid "Backport to support Clang 15 toolchain."
msgstr "向后移植以支持 Clang 15 工具链。"

#: ../../doc/changelog.rst:102
msgid "More utilities."
msgstr "更多实用工具。"

#: ../../doc/changelog.rst:104
msgid ""
"Intermediate interfaces for creating generic wrappers have all moved into"
" the internal namespace, in order to not confuse the users."
msgstr ""
"用于创建通用包装器的中间接口已全部移至内部命名空间，以免混淆用户。"

#: ../../doc/changelog.rst:108 ../../doc/changelog.rst:143
#: ../../doc/changelog.rst:172 ../../doc/changelog.rst:212
#: ../../doc/changelog.rst:251
msgid "Bug fix"
msgstr "错误修复"

#: ../../doc/changelog.rst:110
msgid ""
"Fix error caused by generated default/copy constructor when registering a"
" C array (``type[size]``) as value type."
msgstr ""
"修复在将 C 数组（``type[size]``）注册为值类型时，由生成的默认/拷贝构造函数引起的错误。"

#: ../../doc/changelog.rst:115
msgid ""
"Due to the new lazy evaluation implementation of "
"``script_invoke_result``, it now can only be returned by script "
"invocation tool. User cannot calls its constructor by value directly, "
"e.g., returning a placeholder value when script failed."
msgstr ""
"由于 ``script_invoke_result`` 新的延迟求值实现，它现在只能由脚本调用工具返回。"
"用户不能直接按值调用其构造函数，例如在脚本失败时返回占位符值。"

#: ../../doc/changelog.rst:120
msgid ""
"Please consider converting the code style described above to use "
"``std::optional`` (or ``std::expected`` if C++23 is available)."
msgstr ""
"请考虑将上述代码风格转换为使用 ``std::optional``（如果 C++23 可用，则使用 ``std::expected``）。"

