#: ../../doc/changelog.rst:135
msgid "Update compatibility with AngelScript 2.38.0."
msgstr "更新与 AngelScript 2.38.0 的兼容性。"

#: ../../doc/changelog.rst:136
msgid "Mark more pointers in parameter list by ``const``."
msgstr "在参数列表中标记更多指针为 ``const``。"

#: ../../doc/changelog.rst:137
msgid ""
"Add CMake flag for controlling the warning-as-error compiler flag during "
"development and test."
msgstr ""
"添加 CMake 标志，用于在开发和测试期间控制将警告视为错误的编译器标志。"

#: ../../doc/changelog.rst:138
msgid "Add test for clang-cl (Clang with MSVC-like interfaces) support."
msgstr "添加对 clang-cl（具有类 MSVC 接口的 Clang）支持的测试。"

#: ../../doc/changelog.rst:139
msgid ""
"Add nightly test for checking compatibility of asbind20 with the latest "
"WIP version of AngelScript."
msgstr ""
"添加每日构建测试，用于检查 asbind20 与最新 WIP 版本 AngelScript 的兼容性。"

#: ../../doc/changelog.rst:140
msgid "Add benchmarks for finding performance issues during development."
msgstr "添加在开发过程中发现性能问题的基准测试。"

#: ../../doc/changelog.rst:145
msgid "Add some missing utility interfaces for RAII helpers."
msgstr "为 RAII 辅助函数添加一些缺失的实用接口。"

#: ../../doc/changelog.rst:150
msgid "Update and clarify."
msgstr "更新并澄清。"

#: ../../doc/changelog.rst:151
msgid "Fix typo."
msgstr "修复拼写错误。"

