msgid "1.7.0"
msgstr ""

#: ../../doc/changelog.rst:156
msgid "2025-7-19"
msgstr ""

#: ../../doc/changelog.rst:161
msgid ""
"Fully support of x86 (32bit) Windows platform, including special "
"treatment for ``__stdcall``."
msgstr ""
"全面支持 x86（32位）Windows 平台，包括对 ``__stdcall`` 的特殊处理。"

#: ../../doc/changelog.rst:162
msgid ""
"Binding generator for reference type no longer requires the registered "
"type to be complete type."
msgstr ""
"引用类型的绑定生成器不再要求注册的类型是完整类型。"

#: ../../doc/changelog.rst:163
msgid ""
"Policy for converting script initialization list for constructors "
"accepting ``std::from_range(_t)`` when C++23 is enabled."
msgstr ""
"当启用 C++23 时，用于将脚本初始化列表转换为接受 ``std::from_range(_t)`` 的构造函数的策略。"

#: ../../doc/changelog.rst:168
msgid ""
"Redesign interfaces of ``container::single`` to reduce some surprising "
"behaviours. For example, the destructor won't clean the data, you need to"
" call another function for releasing the data."
msgstr ""
"重新设计 ``container::single`` 的接口以减少一些意外行为。"
"例如，析构函数不会清理数据，你需要调用另一个函数来释放数据。"

#: ../../doc/changelog.rst:174
msgid ""
"Fix mismatched declaration in array extension that may cause crash on x86"
" platform."
msgstr ""
"修复数组扩展中可能导致 x86 平台崩溃的声明不匹配问题。"

#: ../../doc/changelog.rst:175
msgid "Fix CMake error when configuring with Clang 19 toolchain."
msgstr "修复使用 Clang 19 工具链配置时的 CMake 错误。"

#: ../../doc/changelog.rst:180
msgid "Add information about using asbind20 in XMake projects."
msgstr "添加关于在 XMake 项目中使用 asbind20 的信息。"

#: ../../doc/changelog.rst:183
msgid "Removed"
msgstr "移除"

#: ../../doc/changelog.rst:185
msgid ""
"GCC 12 support is dropped due to too many workarounds. Please use GCC 13 "
"or newer."
msgstr ""
"由于需要太多的变通方案，已放弃对 GCC 12 的支持。请使用 GCC 13 或更高版本。"

#: ../../doc/changelog.rst:188
msgid "1.6.0"
msgstr ""

#: ../../doc/changelog.rst:190
msgid "2025-6-14"
msgstr ""

#: ../../doc/changelog.rst:195
msgid "Helper for registering modulo operator."
msgstr "用于注册取模运算符的辅助函数。"

#: ../../doc/changelog.rst:196
msgid "Composite property support."
msgstr "复合属性支持。"

#: ../../doc/changelog.rst:197
msgid ""
"Composite methods support including generic wrapper with or without "
"variable types."
msgstr ""
"复合方法支持，包括带或不带可变类型的通用包装器。"

#: ../../doc/changelog.rst:198
msgid ""
"Official arm64 support. Previously, it works theoretically but not "
"actually tested."
msgstr ""
"官方 arm64 支持。以前，理论上可行但并未实际测试。"

#: ../../doc/changelog.rst:199
msgid ""
"New tools for managing script function without increasing its reference "
"count. It's useful when the programmer has deep understanding about the "
"lifetime and want to write zero overhead code."
msgstr ""
"用于管理脚本函数而不增加其引用计数的新工具。"
"当程序员对生命周期有深入了解并希望编写零开销代码时，这非常有用。"

#: ../../doc/changelog.rst:201
msgid "Adjust file structure for maintenance."
msgstr "调整文件结构以便于维护。"

#: ../../doc/changelog.rst:202
msgid "Slightly optimize memory usage of ``small_vector``."
msgstr "略微优化 ``small_vector`` 的内存使用。"

#: ../../doc/changelog.rst:207
msgid "Removed ``script_function_base``. Use ``script_function<void>`` instead."
msgstr "已移除 ``script_function_base``。请改用 ``script_function<void>``。"

#: ../../doc/changelog.rst:208
msgid ""
"``asbind20::meta::compressed_pair`` changed to "
"``asbind20::compressed_pair``"
msgstr ""
"``asbind20::meta::compressed_pair`` 已更改为 ``asbind20::compressed_pair``"

#: ../../doc/changelog.rst:209
msgid "``asbind20::meta::overloaded`` changed to ``asbind20::overloaded``"
msgstr "``asbind20::meta::overloaded`` 已更改为 ``asbind20::overloaded``"

#: ../../doc/changelog.rst:214
msgid "Update compatibility with ``string_view`` of binding generators."
msgstr "更新与绑定生成器的 ``string_view`` 的兼容性。"

#: ../../doc/changelog.rst:215
msgid ""
"Fix compilation error when using an integer bigger than 8 bytes, such as "
"``__int128`` extension provided by Clang and GCC."
msgstr ""
"修复使用大于 8 字节的整数时的编译错误，例如 Clang 和 GCC 提供的 ``__int128`` 扩展。"

#: ../../doc/changelog.rst:221
msgid "Fix typo and wrong link."
msgstr "修复拼写错误和错误的链接。"

#: ../../doc/changelog.rst:222
msgid "Fix highlight script for AngelScript."
msgstr "修复 AngelScript 的语法高亮脚本。"

#: ../../doc/changelog.rst:223
msgid ""
"Add entrance for extension library for future update. (Currently, the "
"documents of extensions are still incomplete)"
msgstr ""
"为扩展库添加入口以便将来更新。（目前，扩展的文档仍不完整）"

#: ../../doc/changelog.rst:226
msgid "Deprecated"
msgstr "弃用"

#: ../../doc/changelog.rst:228
msgid ""
"Support of GCC 12 will be dropped in the next release, because it "
"requires too many workarounds. Please use GCC 13 or newer."
msgstr ""
"对 GCC 12 的支持将在下一个版本中移除，因为它需要太多的变通方案。请使用 GCC 13 或更高版本。"

#: ../../doc/changelog.rst:231
msgid "1.5.2"
msgstr ""

#: ../../doc/changelog.rst:233
