"Complete support of using AngelScript interfaces within ``AngelScript::``"
" namespace. (Thanks `GitHub @sashi0034 <https://github.com/sashi0034>`_)"
msgstr ""
"完全支持在 ``AngelScript::`` 命名空间中使用 AngelScript 接口。"
"（感谢 `GitHub @sashi0034 <https://github.com/sashi0034>`_）"

