#: ../../doc/changelog.rst:266
msgid "Core Library"
msgstr "核心库"

#: ../../doc/changelog.rst:268
msgid "New tools for binding complex operator overloads"
msgstr "用于绑定复杂运算符重载的新工具"

#: ../../doc/changelog.rst:269
msgid ""
"Interfaces of binding generator now all take ``std::string`` / "
